<section style="padding: 100px 10vw 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column">
        <h1 class="title is-3">Our Project</h1>
        <p> {{title}} is a result of a group project created by three final year students from
          the University of Kent: Imaan Fakim, Norbert Logiewa and Nicolas Valderrabano.
          Through this project, we wanted to created an interdisciplinary platform, giving
          a chance to people to learn and teach subjects they desire. Our user friendly interface
          is for all types of users, from complete beginner to advanced in their field of
          choice.
          <br> We hope you enjoy our website !
        </p>
        <br><br>
        <h2 class="title is-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <h3 class="title is-5">Emails</h3>
        {{#each authors}}
          <p>{{name}}</p>
          <a style="display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;" href="mailto:{{email}}">{{email}}</a>          {{/each}}
        <br><br>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-hidden-mobile">
        <img src="/images/bigLogo.png" width="400" alt="big logo" style="position: relative; bottom: 80px; float: right;">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
